{"tha-ap281:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap281:0.2":"Suvannabibbohanavagga ","tha-ap281:0.3":"9 Ekapundarikattheraapadana ","tha-ap281:1.1":"“Romaso nama namena, ","tha-ap281:1.2":"sayambhu subbato tada; ","tha-ap281:1.3":"Pundarikam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap281:1.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap281:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap281:2.2":"pundarikamadam tada; ","tha-ap281:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap281:2.4":"pundarikassidam phalam. ","tha-ap281:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap281:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap281:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap281:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekapundariko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap281:5.1":"Ekapundarikattherassapadanam navamam. "}